            "text_YpHGz8": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>With a commitment to reversing the biodiversity loss caused by decades of agricultural intensification, Cala Falcó actively regenerates the soil through sustainable farming practices of botanicals. More than a place, it is a living example of how humans can enrich, rather than deplete, the earth.<br/><br/>Cala Falcó and it’s wild botanical farm nurtures and feeds the products that use its powerful natural ingredients. Whether it is our restorative botanical aperitivo ‘Cala Falcó at Spring’ or our Collection of natural holistic wellness products, we harness the power of nature, botanicals and aromacology into each and every one of our Cala Falcó offering.<br/></p><p>We respect the natural rhythms of every plant we cultivate. From wildflowers to native grasses, our botanicals are allowed to grow in harmony with the land. Harvesting and distillation are carried out with care, by hand, either from our wild botanical farm at Cala Falcó or through trusted local farm partners.<br/><br/>These raw materials are then transformed by our scent scientists and master perfumers in our atelier in Palma. The essential oils and extracts we obtain are a direct reflection of this relationship with nature: pure, expressive, and deeply rooted in place.</p><p>We respect the natural rhythms of every plant we cultivate. From wildflowers to native grasses, our botanicals are allowed to grow in harmony with the land. Harvesting and distillation are carried out with care, by hand, either from our wild botanical farm at Cala Falcó or through trusted local farm partners.<br/><br/>These raw materials are then transformed by our scent scientists and master perfumers in our atelier in Palma. The essential oils and extracts we obtain are a direct reflection of this relationship with nature: pure, expressive, and deeply rooted in place.</p>",
